{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Nkav6SfG3gy97rbZYmJADR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GvuzToKYaUPD3b2p39PWXv","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\yemishin\\.squad\\notes\\inbox\\rebecca-W008-2026-03-13.md","content":"# Rebecca W008 — Build & Test Dallas's Latest PR\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-13\n**Task:** W008 — Build and test Dallas's latest PR\n**PR:** PR-4959092 (office-bohemia) — branch `dallas/add-cowork-route`\n**Worktree:** `C:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia-cowork`\n\n## Build Status: ❌ FAIL\n\n### TypeScript Compilation Error\n\n```\nsrc/features/progression/components/CoworkTranscript/CoworkTranscript.tsx:16:1\nTS6133: 'FC' is declared but its value is never read.\n\nimport type { FC } from 'react';\n```\n\nThe `@bebopjs/bebop` package fails typecheck due to an **unused `FC` type import** in `CoworkTranscript.tsx`. Dallas's W009 notes mention removing this import, but it's still present in the committed code — the fix was not applied before pushing.\n\n### Fix Required\n\nRemove line 16 from `apps/bebop/src/features/progression/components/CoworkTranscript/CoworkTranscript.tsx`:\n```diff\n- import type { FC } from 'react';\n```\n\nThis is a one-line fix. Once removed, the build should pass (all 105 other packages in the dependency chain skipped cleanly — only `@bebopjs/bebop` typecheck failed).\n\n## Test Status: ⚠️ No Tests\n\nNo test files (`*.test.*`) exist under `apps/bebop/src/features/progression/`. The feature has zero test coverage. This is a gap that should be addressed before merge.\n\n## PR Scope (16 files, +876 lines)\n\n- **New feature module:** `src/features/progression/` with atoms, components, hooks, types, and index barrel\n- **New route:** `src/routes/_mainLayout.cowork.tsx`\n- **Route tree regenerated:** `src/routeTree.gen.ts`\n- Components: ProgressionCard, UserQuestionBanner, CoworkTranscript, CoworkChat, SuggestionChips\n- State: Jotai atoms for progression steps and user questions\n- Demo hook: `useDemoProgression` for testing without backend\n\n## Learnings\n\n1. **office-bohemia builds are slow but incremental** — Lage cached 105/106 packages. Only the final `@bebopjs/bebop` typecheck ran (~50s). Full pipeline took 1m 4s.\n2. **TypeScript strict mode catches unused imports** — `tsconfig.typecheck.json` enforces `noUnusedLocals`, which is why the unused `FC` import fails the build.\n3. **Existing worktree reuse works** — The `office-bohemia-cowork` worktree from Dallas's earlier work was already at the latest commit and had `node_modules` installed, saving ~13 minutes of `yarn install`.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":794,"cache_read_input_tokens":38860,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":794,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9cb5a381-3127-41e9-8735-a531505f707f","uuid":"9c59336f-4034-4dba-9971-f9bd5729a45d"}
